    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors accepted at Gradation 1 default consistent with MRL 2 scoping. RHI prediction error of 8.3% is within the 15% acceptance threshold established in the V&V plan. The simplified Newtonian model form is noted as a conservative assumption in the simulation plan; the validation results are considered sufficient to support the COU decision. The assessment team concludes that the model provides adequate credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
